    "description": "Dahlia had an ecstatic, once-in-a-lifetime experience on her wedding night. As she longed for that moment to happen again, her married life went on in a dull and painfully monotonous way, until she witnessed her husband’s infidelity. One night, while drunk, her husband slipped on the rooftop and died. At her husband’s funeral, Dahlia suddenly finds herself unjustly accused of murdering him. Then Sebastian, her husband’s identical twin brother, appears before her. Sebastian offers to help her avoid the royal guard’s infamous interrogation, on the condition that she bear his child. When she refuses, he reveals a shocking truth. “Dahlia, do you really believe the man who spent your wedding night with you was Calix?” The truth is, the one who shared that intoxicating wedding night with Dahlia was not her husband, but her brother-in-law.\n\n**Original Webtoon:**    \n[Naver Series](https://series.naver.com/comic/detail.series?productNo=13758423), [Ridibooks](https://ridibooks.com/books/297088177), [Bomtoon](https://www.bomtoon.com/detail/brotherinlawsproxy), [MrBlue](https://www.mrblue.com/webtoon/wt_000076732), [BookCube](https://www.bookcube.com/toon/detail.asp?webtoon_num=260147), [Mootoon](https://www.mootoon.co.kr/comic/moo_list.mg?tcode=avgm), [Qtoon](https://www.qtoon.co.kr/toon/list.mg?tcode=6azo), [Toon365](https://www.toon365.com/domestic/domestic_detail.asp?toon_idx=49143), [ZzangComic](https://www.zzangcomic.co.kr/comic/detailview_comic.asp?comic_idx=52077), [Onestory](https://onestory.co.kr/detail/H049247365), [Nate](https://toonnbook.nate.com/detail/H049247365), [Aladin](https://www.aladin.co.kr/shop/wproduct.aspx?ItemId=388780826), [KyoboBook](https://ebook-product.kyobobook.co.kr/dig/epd/ebook/E000012653155), [Yes24](https://www.yes24.com/product/goods/183640135)",
